                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "interaction",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>When a kylix is holding a drink and not wielding weapons or wearing armor, they're continually protected by a @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.spells-srd.Item.Sanctuary] spell (@Check[will|dc:21]). If the kylix breaks the <em>sanctuary</em> spell, the effect returns if the devil doesn't take any hostile actions for 10 minutes. Additionally, while protected by a <em>sanctuary</em> spell, the kylix can roll Diplomacy for initiative.</p>"
