                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The kylix attempts a @Check[deception], @Check[diplomacy], @Check[performance], or @Check[society] check, and compares their result against the Will DCs of up to four creatures within 60 feet. On a success, these creatures are @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Fascinated] for 1 round. The kylix can Sustain this effect, increasing the duration of this fascination by 1 round for up to 1 minute. When the fascination ends, the affected creatures are then temporarily immune to Courteous Causerie for 1 hour.</p>"
                },
